        "content": "<p>For anyone interested, I will be giving a talk on the formalisation of contemporary additive combinatorics AND on my workflow for contributing to Mathlib. The talk will be given in person in Cambridge at <time datetime=\"2024-12-05T17:00:00Z\">2024-12-05T17:00:00Z</time> and will also be retransmitted on Zoom (and recorded, but I suggest you don't rely on that option since it might be a month before the recording is available)</p>",
